{"tid":1697322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謝振美：不滿獨媒記者「查警暴 止警謊」行動","createTime":"2019-11-06T19:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T01:02:34.000Z","uid":276779,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80a4ca3b0cf7a99f3fcf30adb73b83d0503a7676","tid":1697322,"uid":276779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:26:40.000Z","msg":"【警務處來函<br />\n不滿獨媒記者「查警暴 止警謊」行動】<br />\n<br />\n獨媒晚上收到警務處的電子郵件，稱不滿本網記者參與日前「查警暴，止警謊」的抗議行動。<br />\n<br />\n在電子郵件中，警察再次重複稱，「警方」記者會的目的是要向傳媒解釋政策、澄清及回應傳媒的關注，指記者會場地不是進行示威抗議的地方。<br />\n<br />\n警察又稱，本網記者的行動影響了其他專業記者的採訪權利，和剝削公眾接收警方重要資訊的機會。該封電子郵件由警察公共關係科總警司謝振中代函，同時轉發政府新聞處。<br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n投稿／廣告： info@inmediahk.net<br />\n定額捐款： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2W46Sy2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2W46Sy2&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=aa967161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2W46Sy2</a><br />\nPaypal 單次捐款： <a href=\"http://paypal.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaypal.me%2Finmediahknet&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=349dc02f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">paypal.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GaAJwRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGaAJwRF.jpg&h=9a4d6cbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f8b3e8fedb24896252deecc27d6a73dabc149d3","tid":1697322,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40a07d5d61db9f0dfbe489b8dbbc28f552f95fc1","tid":1697322,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:31:47.000Z","msg":"應該6間都有寄"},{"pid":"a6019ff4e8039d0068c50b9c6f15f1a8d337d0fb","tid":1697322,"uid":276779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T19:31:47.000Z","msg":"皇軍逐間媒體點名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3dfcbe996837032e57c8e